These services include bike paths, road maintenance, and unnecessary docks. Additionally, costly projects such as state troopers and office buildings also contribute to the problem. To address this issue, I would ask my leaders, "How can we cut back on unnecessary expenditures and use the savings to provide more equitable resources for all individuals?"
